{
  "stem": "3382.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There I went-- I remember one thing that during our short sojourn, sojourn in Yelisavetgrad, I used to go to kindergarten.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And now I remember the name of the proprietors of the kindergarten.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was a German or Dutch name-- Van der Flit.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "This is how far my memories go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Of course, there are some other family memories.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "My first very big beating I got because I took apart my sister's doll, who used to say, mama.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As much-- as much as Odessa is concerned-- so in the living room, on one of the walls there was a portrait of Theodor Herzl, and under it, a small table with a Pushkin.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mother used to take me sometimes and say, take a look.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is Jewish king.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I assume-- generally, I assume that we are-- we are a secularized family, but not in the same sense as here they say 'secular.' Because I don't remember going to synagogue in Odessa-- maybe, probably, we went.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I know that my father used to come in a regular suit, you know, like a merchant-- well-to-do merchant, I would say.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His golden, you know, chain was here, or whatever or not.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in Kherson, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I used to get already-- about when I was eight or nine years old, I got a rebbe in Kherson.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Beside that-- so let me start maybe telling you of Kherson, what has happened there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In Kherson, still-- in-- we came probably in Kherson probably about-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] end of 1915, I think, or '16, beginning '16.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there appeared another person in our family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My mother fell in love-- in love with somebody else.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it started to be grudged.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
